---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Learn More — Formic"
  description="News, downloads, mission, and careers — everything beyond the product, in one place."
  ogTitle="Learn More — Formic"
  ogDescription="Mission, news, careers, downloads — Formic beyond the product."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/learn-more" slot="head" />
  <style is:global slot="head">
    .lm-rlist{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:18px 0 0}
    .lm-rlist li{margin:0;padding:0;border-top:1px solid var(--lgrey)}
    .lm-rlist li:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid var(--lgrey)}
    .lm-rlist a{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:16px 0;text-decoration:none;color:var(--black);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.4}
    .lm-rlist a::after{content:'→';color:var(--orange);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0}
    .lm-rlist a:hover{color:var(--orange)}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span>Learn More
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Learn More</div>
    <h1>Driving U.S. manufacturing<br><em>forward</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Why Formic exists, what we're building, and how to get involved: the mission, the news, the resources, and the open roles.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Our mission</div>
      <h2>Accelerate the <em>accessibility</em> of automation.</h2>
      <p>Formic was founded to deliver more capacity, consistency, and reliability to every factory while reducing cost, downtime, and worker safety issues. Every manufacturer deserves access to state-of-the-art automation and a robot workforce without 18-month deployment timelines or capital risk.</p>
      <p>Founded 2020 in Chicago, IL.</p>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Get in touch →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Formic-Team-Photo.jpg" alt="The Formic team posing in front of an American flag — built in Chicago, headquartered in the U.S." loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Founded 2020 · Chicago, IL</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Formic in the news" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Press · Announcements</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">News</div>
      <h2>What we're <em>building</em>.</h2>
      <p>Product launches, customer wins, fundraising milestones, and industry coverage. We post the things that matter.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Latest product releases and platform milestones</li>
        <li>Customer go-live announcements</li>
        <li>Industry coverage and analyst reports</li>
        <li>Media inquiries: press@formic.co</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="mailto:press@formic.co" class="larr">Press inquiries →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Resources</div>
      <h2>The book, the checklists, <em>and the guides</em>.</h2>
      <p>Scope a project, build the business case, or get your team aligned: the resources manufacturers use most before and during an automation evaluation.</p>
      <ul class="lm-rlist">
        <li><a href="https://land.formic.co/automate-now-1">Automate NOW — the guide to getting started with automation</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://land.formic.co/automations-roi-vs-tco-know-the-full-story-before-you-invest">ROI vs TCO — the full story before you invest</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://land.formic.co/palletizer-scoping-checklist">Palletizer scoping checklist</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://land.formic.co/case-packing-quick-start-checklist">Case packing quick-start checklist</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://land.formic.co/5-steps-to-getting-your-team-on-board-with-automation">Five steps to getting your team on board with automation</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-9787.jpg" alt="Formic downloadable resources" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Book · Guides · Checklists</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic careers" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Hiring across engineering &amp; operations</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Careers</div>
      <h2>Build the operating layer of <em>physical industry</em>.</h2>
      <p>We're hiring across engineering, field service, customer success, and operations. Roles based in Chicago and fully remote across the U.S., and we'll relocate the right people.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Robotics &amp; controls engineering</li>
        <li>Field Service Engineers (regional, multiple cities)</li>
        <li>Customer success and account management</li>
        <li>Software, platform, and infrastructure engineering</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="mailto:careers@formic.co" class="larr">See open roles →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Help us automate<br><em>American manufacturing</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="/talk-with-an-expert" class="btn-ctadark">Talk with an Expert</a>
    <a href="mailto:careers@formic.co" class="btn-ctawh">Open Roles</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
